Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:36.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}Who sings this song about us pain and sorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:44.84,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}鏡映しの業を　済ましたふり繕って　見つめてた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:50.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}繰り返す痛み　未だ知らぬ憧れ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:55.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}The weight of my sin nails me down　足搔いても
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:05:00.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}Is it the future falling　偶像崇拝みたいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:05.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}微かな不安の足音を　Despair of all
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:10.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}Emptiness follows you here　This never-ending war
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:16.05,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}信じたい未来へ　巻き戻して
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:23.27,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}赦せなくて　escalateして　escalateして
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:27.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}I need someone to 目を伏せ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:34.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}Pray in my name　太古へ祈って　折れては繋いで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:39.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}Again and again and again　螺旋のよう　one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:44.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}何故戦い続けるの？　まだ捨てきれない物は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:52.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}仮初めか確かな希望か　ふれる針
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:36.64,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}谁在吟咏我们的痛与伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:44.84,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}镜中映射的罪业  虚假的救赎  历历在目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:50.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}反反复复的伤痛  虚无缥缈的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:55.02,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}罪业之重令我难以喘息  挣扎只是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:05:00.56,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}是否这就是未来崩坏  如同偶像崇拜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:05.91,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}那微弱且不安的脚步声  传递出对一切的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:10.94,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}虚无已经找到你了  这没有尽头的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:16.05,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}倒带回想要去相信的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:23.27,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}无法原谅  怒火在上升  在不断上升
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:27.03,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}我需要人们将目光转过去
